{"type": "article", "id": 12689, "title": "Coleman 多功能打火机", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-28T07:28:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122501jxuAaRqdngVlr4YD.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t户外品牌 Coleman 最近推出了一款多功能打火机，除了具备打火机的功能外，它还把小刀，开瓶器，小锉刀，锯齿刀等功能集合在了一起，并且采用防水设计，为户外活动提供了许多的便利，造型看上去也蛮可爱。这款打火机已经正式登陆 Coleman 线上商店，<a href=\"http://www.coleman.com/product/QTR310011#.VbZUTiqqqkq\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140426BkjH94teJodTUOXM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}